{"tid":1817868,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國脫貪？】江蘇省政府聲稱脫貧率99.99%，只剩17人尚未脫貧。","createTime":"2020-01-09T12:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T15:17:34.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"655baf9722694f28a2d37c8b694d2ddfca8d96f1","tid":1817868,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/NewCover-9-990x520.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2FNewCover-9-990x520.jpg&h=fcb0b770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平曾經講過，在2020年，中國將消除絕對貧困；踏入2020年，此話成為全國焦點，中國各地省政府紛紛向中央報告當地的脫貧情況。當中江蘇省在1月7日在南京召開人大會議，江蘇省政府在會上報告了當地的「脫貧攻堅工作」，以及最新發展。<br />\n<br />\n當地政府成立了一個部門，名為「江蘇省政府扶貧辦」，而該辦主任名為朱國兵，他指在過去4年來，省內月入6,000元人民幣以下的低收入人口，有2,542,114人，而他更聲稱其脫貧率達到「99.99%」以上，目前僅有17人尚未脫貧。<br />\n<br />\n朱國兵表示，今年將在強化問題整改，加大攻堅掃尾力度，確保低收入人口全部脫貧、 資金全部撥付到位。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇全省人口超過8,000萬，是中國人多最多的省市之一，當地在2015年發布扶貧目標，以月入6,000元人民幣為標準，針對這些貧窮人口進行一連串的政策支持，當中最主要的對象是農村低收入人口，當中有300萬人左右。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2ce0ca932bcb4476a2f4cbcb2934d38b-990x601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F2ce0ca932bcb4476a2f4cbcb2934d38b-990x601.jpg&h=9e05bd9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有不少網民對「99.99%人口脫貧」感到懷疑，並質疑當局如何計算出「僅17人未脫貧」，數據是否精確等等。當中網民質疑流浪人口如果計算，以及一旦失去政策援助後，會否讓已脫貧的人口再陷入貧窮等等。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/484839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F484839&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF08mKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=e8ba6f74\" target=\"_blank\">https://fortuneinsight.com/web/posts/484839</a>"},{"pid":"d1fd6bda39eaadd7da80a37f58570cc61233e895","tid":1817868,"uid":146535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"一定係啲官，佢地最撚窮嘅"},{"pid":"581571f1ddc9bc90eeac781b10d8479af2dfa740","tid":1817868,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1fd6bda39eaadd7da80a37f58570cc61233e895","tid":1817868,"uid":146535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:19:29.000Z","msg":"一定係啲官，佢地最撚窮嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98133216efcc675ff7d1dc8c576168b3f8115f28","tid":1817868,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"窮人已槍斃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba03f4b12b1dc8a521cc06479f9fa7e644f6e31","tid":1817868,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:23:30.000Z","msg":"果17個最避下風頭<br />\n隨時全省被脫貧"},{"pid":"a5b48f1eb78273a5679e7893d3db894c04dbb616","tid":1817868,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e1752bfde84a4f89111914f37bd215996b1b005b","tid":1817868,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:34:09.000Z","msg":"反正都係吹，點解唔直接話100%脫貧？"},{"pid":"e385060de1835c879a20a60098dcf378889fcda4","tid":1817868,"uid":243855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:36:27.000Z","msg":"作數都唔撚識。。。"},{"pid":"73435ca58070cfc16543b8cd199ed100e582426c","tid":1817868,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"厲害了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fb06b0e323d666f51fb4ff8515806a2436ee8a","tid":1817868,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu